People fight tooth and nail
to get into the Grain Bureau.

00:04:30.431 --> 00:04:31.991
It's in the provincial capital.

00:04:31.991 --> 00:04:33.671
You'll see each other more easily.

00:04:35.111 --> 00:04:35.632
Yeah,

00:04:36.192 --> 00:04:37.952
but I don't want to go there.

00:04:39.152 --> 00:04:39.911
Why not?

00:04:40.632 --> 00:04:42.752
You should go back
to the provincial capital.

00:04:42.911 --> 00:04:44.791
That's where you belong.

00:04:47.231 --> 00:04:49.111
But I want to stay in Pingchuan County.

00:04:49.952 --> 00:04:51.152
Let's talk about it

00:04:51.192 --> 00:04:52.311
after we eat.

00:04:53.351 --> 00:04:55.311
They didn't make you
the Secretary of Yuehai.

00:04:55.791 --> 00:04:57.392
Why do you want to stay in Pingchuan?

00:05:00.551 --> 00:05:01.991
Don't you know

00:05:01.991 --> 00:05:03.032
why she wants to stay?

00:05:03.632 --> 00:05:04.952
You pulled that suicide stunt.

00:05:05.111 --> 00:05:05.431
Now...

00:05:05.431 --> 00:05:06.111
Again?

00:05:06.632 --> 00:05:07.512
You drove me crazy

00:05:07.671 --> 00:05:08.991
and made me do that.

00:05:09.231 --> 00:05:10.671
Can you be reasonable for once?

00:05:11.111 --> 00:05:11.991
Make yourself clear.

00:05:12.072 --> 00:05:12.832
I'm unreasonable?

00:05:14.512 --> 00:05:15.192
Are you going to

00:05:15.272 --> 00:05:16.431
nag about it forever?

00:05:16.471 --> 00:05:16.832
Auntie.

00:05:16.911 --> 00:05:18.072
I want the best for her.

00:05:18.231 --> 00:05:19.192
Is that wrong?

00:05:19.311 --> 00:05:20.072
Auntie, Uncle.

00:05:20.072 --> 00:05:21.032
Be reasonable, okay?

00:05:21.032 --> 00:05:21.671
About what?

00:05:21.671 --> 00:05:22.551
L-Let's calm down.

00:05:22.551 --> 00:05:23.192
Eat first.

00:05:23.231 --> 00:05:24.392
What's your reasoning?

00:05:25.192 --> 00:05:26.072
She's like this.

00:05:26.272 --> 00:05:27.111
Like what?

00:05:27.311 --> 00:05:27.791
This!

00:05:28.032 --> 00:05:29.392
Listen, I just think...

00:05:29.431 --> 00:05:30.192
I think Qiuping

00:05:30.231 --> 00:05:31.431
has her own considerations.

00:05:31.632 --> 00:05:32.871
How about we eat first?

00:05:32.911 --> 00:05:33.231
Yeah.

00:05:33.272 --> 00:05:33.911
Nonsense...

00:05:34.632 --> 00:05:36.392
Mom, lend me your glasses.

00:05:38.752 --> 00:05:39.671
What are you doing?

00:05:41.712 --> 00:05:42.272
Look.

00:05:43.791 --> 00:05:45.351
If I work at the Grain Bureau,

00:05:45.712 --> 00:05:47.272
this is what I'll become.

00:05:47.911 --> 00:05:49.991
Is that what you want for me?

00:05:50.712 --> 00:05:52.152
You... Silly kid.

00:05:54.192 --> 00:05:57.032
Mom, I haven't decided outright
not to go.

00:05:57.431 --> 00:05:58.991
I just found out about this.

00:05:59.471 --> 00:05:59.871
Yeah.

00:06:00.431 --> 00:06:01.871
Let me mull it over

00:06:02.111 --> 00:06:02.991
for a while.

00:06:04.551 --> 00:06:06.231
Alright, let's keep eating.

00:06:07.272 --> 00:06:08.272
Come on.

00:06:11.231 --> 00:06:12.431
Are you taking the job?

00:06:12.911 --> 00:06:13.712
Of course not.

00:06:14.311 --> 00:06:15.111
The way I see it,

00:06:15.832 --> 00:06:18.592
grain coupons and grain shops
will be gone

00:06:19.152 --> 00:06:20.032
in a few years.

00:06:20.752 --> 00:06:23.871
The current way of life will undergo

00:06:23.952 --> 00:06:25.192
drastic changes.

00:06:25.752 --> 00:06:26.752
But if things go on,

00:06:26.791 --> 00:06:28.671
you'll be found out long before then.

00:06:28.832 --> 00:06:29.632
What will you do?

00:06:29.991 --> 00:06:32.111
I'll just say they didn't enroll me.

00:06:33.231 --> 00:06:34.671
Alright. We'll do it your way.

00:06:35.392 --> 00:06:36.111
Thank you.

00:06:39.351 --> 00:06:40.712
I need to tell you something.

00:06:41.192 --> 00:06:43.712
That newly appointed
Secretary Zheng of Yuehai

00:06:43.791 --> 00:06:44.832
contacted us and asked me

00:06:44.991 --> 00:06:46.072
to take some photos

00:06:46.111 --> 00:06:47.632
and write an article for promotion.

00:06:48.231 --> 00:06:51.111
