00:25:23.912 --> 00:25:25.391
I-I have scissors for gauze.

00:25:25.391 --> 00:25:26.232
Lin Dongfu.

00:25:26.272 --> 00:25:27.831
Can I give you some advice, too?

00:25:28.071 --> 00:25:30.071
See, we're taking a group photo

00:25:30.111 --> 00:25:30.831
as cadres.

00:25:30.871 --> 00:25:31.472
The hard hat

00:25:31.512 --> 00:25:32.672
and the tank top?

00:25:33.151 --> 00:25:35.311
Shouldn't we find a collared shirt?

00:25:35.351 --> 00:25:36.992
I need to work after the photo.

00:25:37.032 --> 00:25:38.672
Can we find a collared shirt first?

00:25:38.672 --> 00:25:39.311
Enough.

00:25:39.311 --> 00:25:40.032
Stop arguing.

00:25:40.192 --> 00:25:40.912
Come on.

00:25:41.232 --> 00:25:42.351
Give him his glasses.

00:25:43.311 --> 00:25:44.071
This courtyard

00:25:44.311 --> 00:25:45.391
may look shabby.

00:25:45.912 --> 00:25:47.871
But it has a hundred years of history.

00:25:48.232 --> 00:25:49.432
It's not a famous site.

00:25:49.791 --> 00:25:51.551
But it's a historical site.

00:25:53.111 --> 00:25:54.151
Before liberation,

00:25:54.432 --> 00:25:57.472
this courtyard belonged
to Little Conch's family.

00:25:57.631 --> 00:26:00.311
After liberation,
it became a fireworks factory.

00:26:01.192 --> 00:26:03.272
Now it still belongs
to Little Conch's family.

00:26:03.512 --> 00:26:04.391
I was thinking

00:26:04.591 --> 00:26:06.311
this huge courtyard is sitting empty.

00:26:06.631 --> 00:26:07.232
Let's use it.

00:26:07.512 --> 00:26:09.871
And it'll give him some income. Perfect.

00:26:11.391 --> 00:26:12.232
You're ready?

00:26:12.472 --> 00:26:12.992
Yeah.

00:26:13.232 --> 00:26:14.192
I was thinking

00:26:14.512 --> 00:26:15.432
we should pick

00:26:15.551 --> 00:26:16.952
a meaningful spot for the photo.

00:26:16.992 --> 00:26:18.591
How about the library building?

00:26:19.111 --> 00:26:21.151
It's over a hundred years old.

00:26:21.551 --> 00:26:23.192
After policy restoration,

00:26:23.351 --> 00:26:24.472
we brought many good books.

00:26:24.791 --> 00:26:25.752
Take the photo here.

00:26:25.871 --> 00:26:26.472
- Okay?
- Okay.

00:26:27.111 --> 00:26:28.472
We must ask Guangming's

00:26:28.472 --> 00:26:29.032
opinion.

00:26:29.311 --> 00:26:30.672
The library building is nice.

00:26:31.311 --> 00:26:31.672
Let's go.

00:26:31.672 --> 00:26:32.591
Come on, picture time.

00:26:32.591 --> 00:26:33.351
- Mr. Zheng.
- I can

00:26:33.351 --> 00:26:34.432
even see the bookshelves.

00:26:34.472 --> 00:26:35.351
So many books.

00:26:35.391 --> 00:26:36.432
You must love this.

00:26:37.472 --> 00:26:37.992
Sir.

00:26:38.432 --> 00:26:40.032
Gloves look quite proper.

00:26:40.032 --> 00:26:40.631
No.

00:26:40.631 --> 00:26:41.232
I don't think

00:26:41.232 --> 00:26:41.992
the gloves look...

00:26:41.992 --> 00:26:42.912
Wait, I mean...

00:26:43.351 --> 00:26:44.391
Your haircut looks

00:26:45.032 --> 00:26:46.151
like a dog chewed it off.

00:26:47.071 --> 00:26:47.672
Fine.

00:26:47.672 --> 00:26:48.791
It's better than before.

00:26:48.952 --> 00:26:50.512
Come on, let's take pictures.

00:26:50.752 --> 00:26:52.432
Okay, look over here.

00:26:52.992 --> 00:26:53.831
Try not to blink.

00:26:54.071 --> 00:26:54.432
Okay.

00:26:54.672 --> 00:26:57.032
Come on. One, two, smile.

00:26:58.831 --> 00:26:59.672
Okay, one more shot.

00:27:00.192 --> 00:27:00.712
Wait.

00:27:01.232 --> 00:27:02.871
Let's get Ms. Xiao from the kitchen

00:27:02.992 --> 00:27:04.032
and Little Conch.

00:27:04.232 --> 00:27:04.672
Little Conch.

00:27:04.831 --> 00:27:05.791
I'll get them.

00:27:06.831 --> 00:27:08.591
And tell them to wear

00:27:08.631 --> 00:27:09.272
the uniform.

00:27:09.391 --> 00:27:10.104
Go to the center.

00:27:10.871 --> 00:27:11.432
No way.

00:27:11.912 --> 00:27:12.871
Li, join us.

00:27:13.192 --> 00:27:14.032
Let's take a photo.

00:27:14.032 --> 00:27:14.472
Madam.

00:27:14.472 --> 00:27:15.192
Since you're here.

00:27:15.192 --> 00:27:15.831
No, thanks.

00:27:15.831 --> 00:27:16.151
Come on.

00:27:16.151 --> 00:27:17.192
Since you're here.

00:27:17.432 --> 00:27:18.712
For memories.

00:27:18.712 --> 00:27:19.472
A group photo.

00:27:19.631 --> 00:27:19.992
Right?

00:27:20.151 --> 00:27:20.912
Mr. Du, come on.

00:27:21.151 --> 00:27:21.512
Join us.

00:27:21.551 --> 00:27:22.192
I'll pass.

00:27:22.272 --> 00:27:23.192
Fate brought you here.

00:27:23.192 --> 00:27:24.512
Let's take one together.

00:27:25.071 --> 00:27:26.712
Lin, doesn't the camera have a timer?

00:27:26.752 --> 00:27:27.791
Yeah, it does.

00:27:27.831 --> 00:27:28.591
It's ready.

00:27:28.672 --> 00:27:29.551
Alright, sit down.

00:27:29.591 --> 00:27:30.551
Balance it a bit.

00:27:30.591 --> 00:27:31.071
Come on.

00:27:39.071 --> 00:27:39.551
Okay.

00:27:45.551 --> 00:27:46.912
Come on, Li.

00:27:47.311 --> 00:27:47.912
This way.

00:27:49.631 --> 00:27:50.151
Look.

00:27:50.311 --> 00:27:51.791
This wall is huge.

00:27:51.912 --> 00:27:52.952
Completely blank.

00:27:53.151 --> 00:27:54.752
See the dimensions?

00:27:55.032 --> 00:27:56.351
Perfect size.

00:27:56.551 --> 00:27:59.192
Doesn't it feel like
it's missing something?

00:27:59.192 --> 00:28:00.151
Yeah, it does.

00:28:03.192 --> 00:28:03.712
Sir.

00:28:04.311 --> 00:28:06.192
We might be
thinking the same thing again.

00:28:06.472 --> 00:28:06.871
See?

00:28:08.512 --> 00:28:09.311
Put it right here.

00:28:09.512 --> 00:28:10.871
Right? Today's photo.

00:28:11.151 --> 00:28:13.351
Enlarge it and put it here.

00:28:16.311 --> 00:28:17.432
Problem solved.

00:28:17.551 --> 00:28:18.912
That's it. We have to go now.

00:28:19.351 --> 00:28:19.791
Already?

00:28:19.912 --> 00:28:20.512
Li.

00:28:20.631 --> 00:28:21.712
Wait for me.

00:28:22.232 --> 00:28:22.752
See them out.

00:28:23.071 --> 00:28:24.311
You're clueless.

00:28:28.232 --> 00:28:29.432
Drive safely. Be careful.

00:28:30.272 --> 00:28:31.151
Come visit.

00:28:31.631 --> 00:28:32.512
Stay safe.

00:28:44.791 --> 00:28:45.464
What's wrong?

00:28:48.232 --> 00:28:48.831
Mr. Zheng.

00:28:50.672 --> 00:28:52.151
I never got the chance

00:28:52.631 --> 00:28:53.871
to offer you my gift.

00:28:54.192 --> 00:28:57.071
Congratulations on your election
as the Secretary of Yuehai.

00:29:01.752 --> 00:29:02.512
The blueprint.

00:29:05.272 --> 00:29:07.631
Well....

00:29:08.311 --> 00:29:09.631
I-I'm speechless.

00:29:09.672 --> 00:29:11.712
Thank you so much.

00:29:13.071 --> 00:29:14.672
You've always cared about Yuehai.

00:29:15.791 --> 00:29:17.311
How can I ever repay you?

00:29:37.591 --> 00:29:38.111
Everyone,

00:29:39.032 --> 00:29:40.791
today marks our Yuehai Town Government's

00:29:41.071 --> 00:29:43.712
first full cadre work meeting.

00:29:44.512 --> 00:29:48.192
I requested each of you from the Party.

00:29:49.391 --> 00:29:50.591
I can say without hesitation

00:29:51.111 --> 00:29:53.432
that every one of you
is battle-tested elite

00:29:54.512 --> 00:29:55.992
recognized by the Party.

00:29:56.952 --> 00:29:59.111
Now I'll announce
the Party's appointments.

00:30:09.232 --> 00:30:10.752
Yuehai Town People's Government:

00:30:11.992 --> 00:30:14.232
Following the County's
Party Committee evaluation,

00:30:15.472 --> 00:30:18.591
the following members are appointed
as Yuehai Party Committee members:

00:30:19.512 --> 00:30:21.712
Zheng Decheng is appointed as Secretary,

00:30:22.311 --> 00:30:23.672
overseeing all operations

00:30:24.232 --> 00:30:25.432
in Yuehai.

00:30:25.791 --> 00:30:26.472
- Alright.
- Alright.

00:30:27.272 --> 00:30:27.791
Alright.

00:30:32.712 --> 00:30:33.472
Tan Guangming

00:30:33.912 --> 00:30:35.551
is appointed as deputy mayor,

00:30:35.800 --> 00:30:37.631
supervising finance
and disciplinary affairs.

00:30:37.631 --> 00:30:37.992
Alright.

00:30:38.672 --> 00:30:39.871
Fully expected.

00:30:40.192 --> 00:30:42.032
Make sure you discipline us.

00:30:42.071 --> 00:30:43.912
We can't make mistakes, okay?

00:30:44.071 --> 00:30:44.871
Rest assured.

00:30:45.672 --> 00:30:46.351
Lin Dongfu.

00:30:46.391 --> 00:30:46.712
Here.

00:30:47.232 --> 00:30:48.912
Is appointed as deputy mayor,

00:30:49.176 --> 00:30:51.551
overseeing demolition,
resettlement, and city construction.

00:30:51.551 --> 00:30:52.056
Understood.

00:30:52.591 --> 00:30:52.952
Alright.

00:30:56.871 --> 00:30:59.752
Sir, I'd like to express
some personal opinion.

00:30:59.791 --> 00:31:02.512
It's not that I have any issue with Xie.

00:31:02.712 --> 00:31:04.351
He is highly capable.

00:31:04.631 --> 00:31:05.512
I just feel

00:31:05.672 --> 00:31:08.631
that Lin might be more suitable
for the mayor position.

00:31:08.912 --> 00:31:09.672
He's composed.

00:31:10.391 --> 00:31:11.032
No, I'm not.

00:31:11.831 --> 00:31:12.432
But...

00:31:12.752 --> 00:31:16.391
Xie Chunlai is appointed
as deputy mayor.

00:31:18.752 --> 00:31:19.151
Alright.

00:31:19.791 --> 00:31:21.391
Overseeing personnel and logistics.

00:31:26.551 --> 00:31:28.752
Xie, help me if I get swamped

00:31:28.912 --> 00:31:29.912
with work.

00:31:31.192 --> 00:31:31.992
I-I...

00:31:31.992 --> 00:31:32.992
Well...

00:31:34.512 --> 00:31:35.752
Are you doubting me?

00:31:38.032 --> 00:31:38.591
No, no.

00:31:39.232 --> 00:31:39.791
Well...

00:31:41.712 --> 00:31:43.472
Three deputies?

00:31:43.791 --> 00:31:44.912
Who's in charge?

00:31:45.071 --> 00:31:46.432
He's right, sir.

00:31:46.472 --> 00:31:47.871
Who is the town mayor?

00:31:48.311 --> 00:31:49.712
I know what you're thinking.

00:31:50.311 --> 00:31:51.631
The higher-ups

00:31:52.192 --> 00:31:53.631
haven't finalized it yet.

00:31:54.151 --> 00:31:55.151
But rest assured,

00:31:55.952 --> 00:31:56.472
I promise

00:31:56.712 --> 00:31:59.472
the result will come out soon, okay?

00:31:59.512 --> 00:31:59.871
Alright.

00:32:00.351 --> 00:32:01.432
Sit down first.

00:32:01.752 --> 00:32:02.272
Easy.

00:32:02.512 --> 00:32:03.591
Listen to the leader.

00:32:03.631 --> 00:32:03.992
Okay?

00:32:04.912 --> 00:32:06.472
So, let's first discuss

00:32:06.512 --> 00:32:11.831
the specific work arrangements
for Yuehai's city construction, okay?

00:32:12.791 --> 00:32:13.311
Sir.

00:32:13.631 --> 00:32:14.591
I must emphasize

00:32:14.712 --> 00:32:16.432
that I can't agree with it.

00:32:16.672 --> 00:32:17.712
Seriously, I can't.

00:32:17.952 --> 00:32:18.712
On what?

00:32:19.311 --> 00:32:20.032
(In fact,)

00:32:20.712 --> 00:32:22.952
(building Yuehai City
faced numerous obstacles.)

00:32:23.912 --> 00:32:26.672
(I didn't know how they could
complete such a daunting task.)

00:32:28.432 --> 00:32:31.351
(That night, they seemed to argue
for a long time.)

00:32:32.791 --> 00:32:34.351
(But the next time I saw them,)

00:32:35.672 --> 00:32:36.712
(they were in trouble.)

00:32:40.391 --> 00:32:41.871
What? Selling land?

00:32:42.551 --> 00:32:43.111
Mr. Zhao.

00:32:43.752 --> 00:32:44.952
The Constitution stipulates

00:32:44.952 --> 00:32:47.512
that city land belongs to the state
and can't be traded.

00:32:48.272 --> 00:32:49.512
We have received reports

00:32:50.032 --> 00:32:52.631
that the Yuehai Town Government
might be trading land.

00:32:53.912 --> 00:32:54.672
Is there evidence?

00:32:55.591 --> 00:32:56.712
I know Zheng Decheng.

00:32:56.912 --> 00:32:58.512
He wouldn't make such a mistake.

00:33:00.151 --> 00:33:01.071
Mr. Zhao, look.

00:33:01.512 --> 00:33:02.952
We've gathered some information.

00:33:04.752 --> 00:33:06.432
Here are the land certificates

00:33:07.071 --> 00:33:07.591
they issued.

00:33:08.311 --> 00:33:09.071
The receipts.

00:33:09.432 --> 00:33:10.791
Amount and location

00:33:10.791 --> 00:33:11.391
are stated.

00:33:12.712 --> 00:33:15.591
These complaint letters
came from the Public Complaints Office

00:33:15.992 --> 00:33:17.912
(City Construction Fee)
accusing Yuehai of illegal land trading.

00:33:18.351 --> 00:33:19.192
Take a look.

00:33:19.591 --> 00:33:20.831
These land certificates

00:33:20.952 --> 00:33:22.232
represent plots of land.

00:33:23.071 --> 00:33:24.311
It's illegal land trading.

00:33:24.591 --> 00:33:25.992
T-This is outrageous.

00:33:26.591 --> 00:33:27.472
It sounds clear.

00:33:28.752 --> 00:33:29.712
Come on, sit down.

00:33:30.432 --> 00:33:30.912
Sit down.

00:33:31.992 --> 00:33:33.752
Li, take a look.

00:33:35.151 --> 00:33:35.712
Mr. Zhao.

00:33:36.032 --> 00:33:38.752
I suggest we investigate first.

00:33:39.311 --> 00:33:40.791
Let's not jump to conclusions.

00:33:41.472 --> 00:33:43.311
Everyone, I don't think we should

00:33:43.672 --> 00:33:46.151
elevate this
to the level of unconstitutionality

00:33:46.591 --> 00:33:48.591
before a thorough investigation.

00:33:48.952 --> 00:33:51.871
Of course, we can't jump to conclusions.

00:33:52.111 --> 00:33:53.871
We must rely on facts and evidence.

00:33:54.712 --> 00:33:57.952
Sir, we need to
handle this matter promptly.

00:33:59.111 --> 00:34:00.472
There will be trouble

00:34:00.952 --> 00:34:01.831
if it escalates.

00:34:08.591 --> 00:34:10.591
I propose we form an investigation team

00:34:11.711 --> 00:34:13.912
on the suspected illegal land trading.

00:34:14.231 --> 00:34:14.671
I agree.

00:34:15.432 --> 00:34:16.432
- Agreed.
- I agree.

00:34:16.992 --> 00:34:17.912
- I agree.
- Agreed.

00:34:19.872 --> 00:34:21.352
The investigation team

00:34:22.912 --> 00:34:24.184
will consist of Cai Gang...

00:34:27.032 --> 00:34:28.872
and Li Qiuping.

00:34:30.271 --> 00:34:31.231
Cai Gang,

00:34:31.231 --> 00:34:32.231
you'll be in charge...

00:34:32.352 --> 00:34:32.952
Sir,

00:34:33.392 --> 00:34:35.992
I'm in a sensitive position

00:34:36.751 --> 00:34:37.671
for this task.

00:34:38.032 --> 00:34:39.551
Well...

00:34:43.872 --> 00:34:45.231
Li Qiuping will be the leader.

00:34:45.512 --> 00:34:47.992
Cai Gang will assist her.

00:34:48.271 --> 00:34:49.151
Look into it.

00:34:49.432 --> 00:34:50.512
Keep the DIC updated

00:34:51.671 --> 00:34:52.711
at all times.

00:34:53.472 --> 00:34:55.111
Take the local police Tian Haiyang.

00:34:55.352 --> 00:34:57.032
Safeguard the people's property.

00:34:57.992 --> 00:34:58.512
Alright.

00:34:58.912 --> 00:34:59.512
No problem.

00:34:59.912 --> 00:35:00.352
Li.

00:35:00.711 --> 00:35:02.711
I don't care what you think.

00:35:03.271 --> 00:35:06.792
But you must be objective and impartial.

00:35:07.191 --> 00:35:07.952
Don't let me down.

00:35:08.832 --> 00:35:09.751
Rest assured, sir.

00:35:39.312 --> 00:35:39.952
Li.

00:35:40.872 --> 00:35:42.312
I'm from the county police office.

00:35:42.792 --> 00:35:43.591
We're here on duty.

00:35:44.071 --> 00:35:45.872
Please stop what you're doing.

00:35:45.992 --> 00:35:47.392
Please cooperate. Please stop.

00:35:48.352 --> 00:35:49.111
What...

00:35:49.512 --> 00:35:50.992
Mr. Zheng, good to see you again.

00:35:51.551 --> 00:35:52.312
Let's talk outside.

00:35:59.071 --> 00:36:00.271
What are you doing?

00:36:00.912 --> 00:36:01.512
Sir,

00:36:01.952 --> 00:36:03.671
DIC and the County Party Committee

00:36:03.832 --> 00:36:05.872
sent us to investigate the land trading.

00:36:06.432 --> 00:36:08.671
They want this investigation
concluded swiftly.

00:36:08.872 --> 00:36:11.551
We hope you can
help us complete this task

00:36:11.832 --> 00:36:13.111
as soon as possible.

00:36:13.312 --> 00:36:14.591
You're here to investigate us?

00:36:14.751 --> 00:36:15.151
Yes.

00:36:16.032 --> 00:36:17.151
We've received reports

00:36:17.392 --> 00:36:19.231
that you are involved in land dealings.

00:36:19.472 --> 00:36:20.352
What land dealings?

00:36:20.591 --> 00:36:21.792
Yeah, that's nonsense.

00:36:21.992 --> 00:36:23.071
We haven't sold any land.

00:36:23.071 --> 00:36:23.671
Not at all.

00:36:23.711 --> 00:36:24.551
Who said that?

00:36:24.631 --> 00:36:25.952
- Who said that?
- Take a look.

00:36:25.952 --> 00:36:26.792
Enough.

00:36:28.751 --> 00:36:29.472
We'll cooperate.

00:36:46.551 --> 00:36:46.952
Go ahead.

00:36:48.832 --> 00:36:49.551
You talk.

00:36:51.032 --> 00:36:53.032
You said we were selling land.

00:36:53.191 --> 00:36:54.071
Do you have proof?

00:36:58.071 --> 00:36:59.392
You're talking to me first.

00:37:01.032 --> 00:37:02.711
You recognize my importance here.

00:37:03.111 --> 00:37:04.271
Thank you for your trust.

00:37:05.551 --> 00:37:08.832
Let me tell you
how this money came about.

00:37:09.392 --> 00:37:11.352
We secured such a large sum

00:37:12.111 --> 00:37:15.231
due to people's trust
in our entire leadership team.

00:37:15.512 --> 00:37:16.631
We collected money

00:37:16.792 --> 00:37:17.912
for something important.

00:37:18.151 --> 00:37:20.231
This is the city construction fee.

00:37:22.392 --> 00:37:23.151
Yes, write it down.

00:37:23.352 --> 00:37:24.472
City construction fee.

00:37:24.912 --> 00:37:25.751
Mind your business.

00:37:28.032 --> 00:37:30.352
These farming households
bring their hard-earned money

00:37:30.631 --> 00:37:31.271
and ask

00:37:31.631 --> 00:37:34.711
to settle down in the city
we're going to build.

00:37:35.111 --> 00:37:37.151
They want to build Yuehai
together with us.

00:37:37.432 --> 00:37:38.191
What's the problem?

00:37:41.432 --> 00:37:42.312
What should I say?

00:37:45.432 --> 00:37:46.032
Are you done?

00:37:46.392 --> 00:37:47.071
Not yet.

00:37:47.512 --> 00:37:50.271
Every single fee has a clear record.

00:37:51.352 --> 00:37:52.032
Mr. Xie.

00:37:52.271 --> 00:37:52.992
If you're done,

00:37:53.071 --> 00:37:54.071
I have some questions.

00:37:54.392 --> 00:37:55.512
Just answer them.

00:38:15.032 --> 00:38:15.551
Mr. Lin.

00:38:16.151 --> 00:38:16.671
I...

00:38:16.992 --> 00:38:17.472
Please sit.

00:38:21.631 --> 00:38:22.271
Mr. Lin,

00:38:22.792 --> 00:38:24.591
why are you collecting money?

00:38:24.872 --> 00:38:25.592
To build roads.

00:38:32.312 --> 00:38:34.151
We're planning to build this one,

00:38:34.392 --> 00:38:35.832
this one, and this one.

00:38:36.551 --> 00:38:37.231
And then,

00:38:37.591 --> 00:38:39.151
we plan to build roads here, here,

00:38:39.312 --> 00:38:39.952
and here.

00:38:40.591 --> 00:38:41.271
All these places.

00:38:42.231 --> 00:38:44.191
From the seashore to the mountain foot.

00:38:44.352 --> 00:38:45.432
We will build many roads.

00:38:46.032 --> 00:38:48.056
The main arteries
will be 30 meters wide at least

00:38:48.151 --> 00:38:50.432
to handle future traffic congestion.

00:38:51.032 --> 00:38:51.711
- So...
- Mr. Lin,

00:38:52.392 --> 00:38:53.472
I know what you're saying.

00:38:54.111 --> 00:38:55.071
I drew this map.

00:39:05.992 --> 00:39:06.472
Yu.

00:39:09.392 --> 00:39:09.992
Your turn.

00:39:11.151 --> 00:39:11.711
Quiet.

00:39:21.392 --> 00:39:22.032
Leaders,

00:39:22.591 --> 00:39:23.751
I don't know anything.

00:39:24.032 --> 00:39:24.832
Yu Qingtian.

00:39:25.392 --> 00:39:26.952
Answer our questions.

00:39:27.671 --> 00:39:29.472
Aren't you a member
of the town government?

00:39:29.631 --> 00:39:30.671
I never wanted to come.

00:39:31.071 --> 00:39:32.512
If you don't believe me,

00:39:32.711 --> 00:39:33.832
ask Minister Guan.

00:39:34.231 --> 00:39:35.832
They came to my home

00:39:35.832 --> 00:39:36.551
and asked for me.

00:39:36.952 --> 00:39:38.352
My parents agreed to it.

00:39:39.191 --> 00:39:39.872
Leaders,

00:39:40.512 --> 00:39:41.751
