00:41:12.591 --> 00:41:13.392
For how much money?

00:41:15.151 --> 00:41:16.912
Wait, leaders...

00:41:17.912 --> 00:41:19.992
Since you are investigating

00:41:20.271 --> 00:41:24.071
on behalf of the county DIC
and the County Party Committee,

00:41:24.111 --> 00:41:26.912
don't you think
it's premature to label it just yet?

00:41:27.231 --> 00:41:28.631
We weren't trading land.

00:41:28.711 --> 00:41:30.912
We were collecting
the city construction fee.

00:41:31.071 --> 00:41:32.912
And it's all reflected in the accounts.

00:41:32.952 --> 00:41:35.151
Every single payment received
is recorded there.

00:41:35.432 --> 00:41:36.472
City construction fee.

