00:42:01.151 --> 00:42:04.231
You collected money for more plots
than there are resident households.

00:42:05.111 --> 00:42:05.992
I can explain that.

00:42:06.832 --> 00:42:07.231
Indeed,

00:42:07.912 --> 00:42:08.912
as of now,

00:42:09.032 --> 00:42:11.792
there are over 1,200 households.

00:42:12.032 --> 00:42:14.512
But everyone's needs are different.

00:42:14.792 --> 00:42:17.872
Some households might need two, three,

00:42:17.912 --> 00:42:19.191
or even four plots.

00:42:19.231 --> 00:42:21.792
Some have multiple generations
under one roof,

00:42:21.992 --> 00:42:23.432
