00:42:48.151 --> 00:42:48.751
I did.

00:42:50.912 --> 00:42:51.952
The economy is struggling.

00:42:52.711 --> 00:42:54.151
We lack funds for city construction.

00:42:54.631 --> 00:42:57.151
So, after deliberation
by the town Party committee,

00:42:57.711 --> 00:43:00.631
we decided to collect
a city construction fee.

